<section xml:id="sec-properties-of-logarithms" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">

    <title>Properties of Logarithms</title>
    <p>
        In this section, we'll investigate some important properties of logarithms, which will help us to be able to solve exponential and logarithmic equations.
    </p>

    <paragraphs>
        <title>Textbook Reference</title>
        <p> 
            This relates to content in <section-mark/>3.5 of 
            <url href="https://openstax.org/details/books/algebra-and-trigonometry-2e" visual="http://tiny.cc/111Z-Textbook">Algebra and Trigonometry 2e</url>.
        </p>
    </paragraphs>

    <exercises xml:id="prep-log-properties">
        <exercise>
            <introduction>
                <p>
                    Simplify each numerical expression without a calculator. Then state the corresponding exponent rule.
                </p>
            </introduction>
            <task>
                <statement>
                    <p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><m>8^1</m></li>
                            <li><m>b^1</m></li>
                        </ul>
                    </p>
                </statement>
            </task>
            <task>
                <statement>
                    <p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><m>7^0</m></li>
                            <li><m>b^0</m></li>
                        </ul>
                    </p>
                </statement>
            </task>
            <task>
                <statement>
                    <p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><m>6^{-2}</m></li>
                            <li><m>b^{-n}</m></li>
                        </ul>
                    </p>
                </statement>
            </task>
            <task>
                <statement>
                    <p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><m>5^2 \cdot 5^9</m></li>
                            <li><m>b^n \cdot b^m</m></li>
                        </ul>
                    </p>
                </statement>
            </task>
            <task>
                <statement>
                    <p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><m>\dfrac{4^7}{4^3}</m></li>
                            <li><m>\dfrac{b^n}{b^m}</m></li>
                        </ul>
                    </p>
                </statement>
            </task>
            <task>
                <statement>
                    <p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><m>\left(3^2\right)^5</m></li>
                            <li><m>\left(b^n\right)^m</m></li>
                        </ul>
                    </p>
                </statement>
            </task>
        </exercise>
